@startuml GenericSequenceDiagramUpdateX
title Level 1 Sequence Diagram (SD) - Update Feature
autonumber

actor ":User" as User
participant ":System" as System


User -> System: Initiates update (e.g. clicks edit)
activate System

System -->> User: Displays edit form with pre-filled data

User -> System: Submits updated form

alt Resource updated successfully
    System -->> User: Shows success toast

else Resource with {id} does not exist
    System -->> User: Shows error: Resource not found

else Invalid data provided
    System -->> User: Shows error: Invalid data / Business rule violation
end

deactivate System

@enduml